  "title": "Customer Service Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us:</strong></p><p>Meat Co. is a leading importer and distributor of high-quality meat products, proudly serving the hospitality industry. We supply premium cuts to Hotels, Supermarkets, and Restaurants, ensuring freshness, consistency, and service excellence every time.</p><p><strong>Position Summary:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a proactive and customer-focused <strong>Customer Service Executive</strong> to join our team. The ideal candidate will play a crucial role in ensuring a seamless customer experience by handling incoming orders, addressing customer inquiries and complaints, and coordinating internally to support timely deliveries and customer satisfaction.<br /><br />Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Receive and process customer orders via phone, email, and online platforms.</p></li><li><p>Handle customer inquiries and complaints in a professional and timely manner.</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate records of customer interactions and transactions, including entering and issuing invoices.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal departments (e.g., logistics, sales, and warehouse teams) to ensure customer orders are fulfilled accurately and on time.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients, understanding their preferences and business needs.</p></li><li><p>Monitor and follow up on deliveries to ensure client satisfaction.</p></li><li><p>Escalate unresolved issues to the appropriate internal teams and follow through to resolution.</p></li><li><p>Provide feedback to management on customer concerns, service issues, or process improvements.</p></li></ul><h2>Unlock job insights</h2>",
